        <mxCell id="note_text" value="&#xa;Key Features:&#xa;&#xa;• Static Analysis: Cppcheck, CodeQL&#xa;• Dynamic Analysis: LibFuzzer&#xa;• Async Processing: Celery + Redis&#xa;• Containerization: Docker&#xa;• Orchestration: Kubernetes&#xa;• Monitoring: Prometheus + Grafana&#xa;• Database: SQLite (scans)&#xa;• Future: RAG for LLM patching&#xa;&#xa;Data Flow:&#xa;1. User submits code via Web UI&#xa;2. Static analysis finds vulnerabilities&#xa;3. Fuzz plan generated from findings&#xa;4. Harnesses auto-generated&#xa;5. Fuzzing executed in containers&#xa;6. Crashes triaged and analyzed&#xa;7. Repro kits generated&#xa;8. Results displayed in dashboard&#xa;&#xa;Infrastructure:&#xa;• Docker Compose for local dev&#xa;• Kubernetes for production&#xa;• Prometheus scrapes metrics&#xa;• Grafana visualizes data&#xa;• Redis handles task queue&#xa;• SQLite stores scan data" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
